â””â”€â”€ README.mdsee a stadard pattern?we are building a production level app remeber?or why did u do it like thatAcknowledged architectural critique and proposed collaborative refactoring strategy.Oh snap! He's absolutely right. I just gave him a single-file FastAPI app like a tutorial example, not a production-grade structure. He's calling me out - and he SHOULD.
